00:31:09,099 --> 00:31:10,538
Maafkan saya.

366
00:31:10,587 --> 00:31:12,687
Di manakah bilik guru?

367
00:31:16,634 --> 00:31:18,034
Terima kasih.

368
00:31:51,518 --> 00:31:52,918
Jumpa awak.

369
00:31:53,604 --> 00:31:55,034
Hai, Haru.

370
00:31:57,611 --> 00:31:59,181
Hai, Dan Oh.

371
00:32:11,092 --> 00:32:13,148
Haru, bila awak sebut
nama saya seperti,

372
00:32:13,703 --> 00:32:15,000
"Dan Oh.".

