00:34:35,586 --> 00:34:37,215
dengan kekasih saya.

431
00:34:37,993 --> 00:34:39,503
Itu hasrat saya.

432
00:34:42,272 --> 00:34:43,672
Haru.

433
00:34:44,127 --> 00:34:45,527
Haru.

434
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:50,614
Kenapa awak pandang saya?

