suka jika awak ada di sana...

564
00:49:11,917 --> 00:49:13,117
Apa? Helo?

565
00:49:13,142 --> 00:49:14,642
Helo?

566
00:49:15,974 --> 00:49:17,374
Dia hubungi saya secara tiba-tiba...

567
